Enum Phrase

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Phrase>
      • main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.Phrase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Phrase>

    public enum Phrase
extends Enum<Phrase>
    Phrase contains every message that is used in placeholders or commands. The contents for each message can be changed. Every message can contain a String or ChatColor.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Rsl1122
